Class ConnectorUserMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uplanet.lucy.server.odata.connector.api.cfg.ConnectorUserMapping
  • public final class ConnectorUserMapping
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides user mappings between Intrexx users and external system users. Usually required for static authentication and impersonation/delegation purposes.
